{{multiple image|caption_align=center|header_align=center| align = right| direction = vertical| width = 200| header = 1799 two-decimes essai coin | footer=<center>Three separate strikes of the proposed two-decimes coin (not adopted)|image1 = France 1799 2 Decimes (pattern).jpg | alt1 = | caption1 = | image2 = France 1799 2 Decimes (pattern, obverse).jpg | alt2 = | caption2  =| image3 = France 1799 2 Decimes (pattern, reverse).jpg | alt3 = | caption3  =  }}
'''Essai''' is an alternative term for a [[pattern coin]]. Essai is found on coins of [[France]] and of many other French-speaking countries. 'Essai' is also inscribed on the pattern coins of [[Namibia]] along with the word 'Probe'.

