'''Joel Baer Falkovich''' was a [[Russian Empire]] dramatist. He authored Yiddish plays such as ''Reb Chaimele der Koẓin'', ([[Odessa]], 1866) and ''Rochel die Singerin'', ([[Zhytomyr]], 1868). His letters to [[Abraham Firkovich]] were also noted.<ref name="WalfishKizilov2010">{{cite book|last1=Walfish|first1=Barry Dov|last2=Kizilov|first2=Mikhail|title=Bibliographia Karaitica: An Annotated Bibliography of Karaites and Karaism. Karaite Texts and Studies|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7M0_Ba0lDjwC&pg=PA484|accessdate=8 September 2012|date=17 December 2010|publisher=BRILL|isbn=978-90-04-18927-0|page=484}}</ref>
