{{Infobox language |name=Mbudum |nativename=''Mbədam'' |states=[[Cameroon]] |region=[[Far North Province]] |ethnicity= |speakers=6,000 |date=2001 |ref=e18 |familycolor=Afro-Asiatic |fam2=[[Chadic languages|Chadic]] |fam3=[[Biu–Mandara languages|Biu–Mandara]] |fam4=[[Daba languages|Daba]] (A.7) |fam5=South |iso3=xmd |glotto=mbed1242 |glottorefname=Mbedam }}
'''Mbudum''' or '''Mbədam''' is an [[Afro-Asiatic languages|Afro-Asiatic]] language spoken in [[Cameroon]] in [[Far North Province]].<ref name=e18/>
