va]] |Dialogues |- |[[Rettai Jadai Vayasu|Rettai jadai vayasu]] |1997 |Tamil |Siva kumar |Dialogues |- |[[Mahaprabhu (film)|Mahaprabhu]] |1996 |Tamil |[[A. Venkatesh (director)|A. Venkatesh]] |Dialogues |}
